—ظTarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/run-external.mdظ@0c6f3437b84c359ceefe3a208c1e3005885cf50be319d455d592a830108bf4f6³title: run-external‘¨Examplesع|Run an external command
